-1994x1653.png 1994w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-13-at-5.09.20-PM-600x497.png 600w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/Screen-Shot-2021-04-13-at-5.09.20-PM-500x414.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2678px) 100vw, 2678px\" /><figcaption>The Shortcode Block support the calendar shortcodes offered in Events Calendar Pro.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With a few tweaks here and there using Kadence&#8217;s wide variety of settings, we can make a slick calendar page.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"2418\" height=\"5132\" src=\"https://s3.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2266795\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar.png 2418w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-141x300.png 141w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-482x1024.png 482w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-40x85.png 40w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-768x1630.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-724x1536.png 724w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-965x2048.png 965w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-430x913.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-645x1369.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-2000x4245.png 2000w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-1068x2267.png 1068w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-460x976.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-1602x3400.png 1602w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-1074x2279.png 1074w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-512x1087.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-1611x3419.png 1611w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-519x1102.png 519w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-250x530.png 250w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-779x1653.png 779w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-300x637.png 300w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-377x800.png 377w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/wp-kadence-tec-calendar-500x1061.png 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2418px) 100vw, 2418px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"h-creating-event-pages-with-kadence-blocks\">Creating event pages with Kadence Blocks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, there&#8217;s blocks. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/kadence-blocks/\">Kadence Blocks</a> is a massive (and free!) collection of elements that can be dropped into the block editor and arranged to create layouts. Even better, <a href=\"https://www.kadenceblocks.com/prebuilt-library/\">Kadence Blocks include a bunch of pre-built designs</a> that make creating pages fast and easy. You can think of them as <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/blog/wordpress/how-to-work-with-wordpress-block-patterns/\">block patterns:</a> They&#8217;re reusable groups of blocks that form layout components.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"2226\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/wddsiy1na/uploads/2021/04/kadence-blocks-patterns-1.png\" alt=\"Three tiles in a row, each with a screenshot of different Kadence block patterns: header (left), three card panel (center), and a two-button call to action (right).\" class=\"wp-