caption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Kadence Blocks are the <em>perfect</em> tool for making beautiful and engaging event pages. They work with events, giving you full control to make the page look however you want!</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img width=\"2060\" height=\"3478\" src=\"https://ik.imagekit.io/wddsiy1na/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2267066\" srcset=\"https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout.png 2060w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-178x300.png 178w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-607x1024.png 607w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-50x85.png 50w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-768x1297.png 768w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-910x1536.png 910w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-1213x2048.png 1213w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-430x726.png 430w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-645x1089.png 645w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-2000x3377.png 2000w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-1068x1803.png 1068w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-460x777.png 460w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-1602x2705.png 1602w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-1074x1813.png 1074w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-512x864.png 512w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-1611x2720.png 1611w, https://images.theeventscalendar.com/uploads/2021/04/kadence-event-layout-653x1102.png 653w,